                  h3 Jade: A templating language
                  p.talk-summary
                    | Jade is a popular templating engine for JavaScript.
                    | Built primarily for server side use but with support
                    | for use in the client as well, it is performant,
                    | terse and powerful.
                    br
                    | This talk will introduce the jade templating language,
                    | explain the design choices in the language and cover
                    | the changes that are coming in version 1.0.0.
                    | It will also discuss best practices for inheritance,
                    | mixins, filters etc.
                td.time 14:50
