                      img(src='/img/speakers/lenny-markus.jpg')
                  h3 Building for scale with KrakenJS
                  p.talk-summary
                    | A member of the KrakenJS core team will explain
                    | the philosophy behind the framework, why it's a
                    | good fit for large and small companies; and build
                    | a complete application -live- as you are guided
                    | through the most important features of the framework.
                td.time 15:35
