                td.time 16:10
                td.talk(colspan="2")
                  .pictures
                    a(href='/#Jú Gonçalves', title='Jú Gonçalves')
                      img(src='/img/speakers/ju-goncalves.jpg')
                  h3 Improving client-side apps' performance with Facebook's React
                  p.talk-summary
                    | React uses advanced algorithmics together with
                    | reactive programming to make it easier to create
                    | faster UIs, by reducing the amount of DOM manipulations.
                    br
                    | Doesn't it matter if you app is Backbone or Angular based,
                    | this talk will show why (and how) add React to your project.
                    | It will also introduce Om, for the ones who needs very
                    | performant apps, by taking advantage of the concept of
                    | immutability.
                td.time 16:10
