                  h3 Promises and Generators: control flow utopia
                  p.talk-summary
                    | I will talk about how ES6 generators can help you
                    | make your asynchronous code easier to understand in
                    | terms of synchronous concepts and how you can get
                    | some of the same benefits in thought processes by
                    | using promises today.  I will also discuss the
                    | ES6 promises specification.
