                  h3 Be MEAN
                  p.talk-summary
                    | Actually we can do anything with Javascript, so why
                    | not make an entire application with Javascript? It's
                    | for that MEAN exists, we can use MongoDb, Express,
                    | AngularJs and Node.js for create several applications,
                    | let's know how integrate all this technologies.
                td.workshop(rowspan=4)
                 .pictures
