                  h3(title='Exceeding expectations: how the MontageJS Draw cycle helps HTML5 apps rival the native experience')
                    | MontageJS
                  p.talk-summary
                    | Delivering complex mobile experiences with HTML5 that
                    | match consumers high expectations is still very
                    | challenging. This talk explains how the Draw Cycle
                    | in the MontageJS open source HTML5 Framework minimizes
                    | expensive layout reflows to provide high quality user
                    | experience, particularly on mobile devices...
