                  h3 A future called Web Components
                  p.talk-summary
                    | Discover how this new concept formed by
                    | five new W3C specifications (Templates,
                    | Decorators, Shadow DOM, Custom Elements,
                    | HTML Imports) will revolutionize the way
                    | we develop and interact on the web.
                td.workshop(rowspan=5)
