                  h3 Source Maps, how they work and why you should care
                  p.talk-summary
                    | Most of us are using source maps one way or the other and
                    | pretty much every web developer will encounter them sooner
                    | or later. It's time to get a good grasp on them.
                    br
                    | You may know that source maps come into play when
                    | transpiling, bundling or minifying JavaScript, but
                    | did you know that they also made their way into
                    | css transpilers like sass?
                    br
                    | The talk will be structured into the below sections
                    | designed to give attendees a full understanding on
                    | how source maps work and hopefully inspire them to
                    | write more awesome tools that make use of them.
                td.time 14:35
